Still good but weird. Mozzarella sticks or spinach dip.  The potato skins aren't skins they have potato in them, which most places do; but these are allot of potato and they skimp on the cheese and bacon so wouldn't recommend... If your looking for at least a half decent skin. Not here! We get the ribs, miss the Jack Daniels ribs, but these are good just inconsistent.  Sometimes you get allot of sauce cooked in them and sometime barely any   So if you get it to go, always ask for a side of sauce. Again notice the variety and will say allot of times we go and just order a bunch of apps as there is so many to choose from.  Then order ribs to go.
